 Louis VIII of France attacked Poitou and northern Gascony.","jurisdictionLevel":2},{"id":1705189,"age":74,"year":"1259","julianDay":2180901,"title":"100 Years of Conflict Between England and France Ends","description":"Treaty of Paris was signed on December 4, 1259, which ended 100 years of conflict between England and France.","url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Treaty_of_Paris_(1259)","urlTitle":"Wikipedia - Treaty of Paris 1259","jurisdictionLevel":2},{"id":1705190,"age":105,"year":"1290","julianDay":2192224,"title":"Jews Expelled From England","description":"After years of anti-Semitic behavior, King Edward I expelled Jews from England in 1290.","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"When William de Tracy was born in 1185, in Toddington, Gloucestershire, England, his father, William de Tracy, was 52 and his mother, Hawise Bourne, was 48. He married Mrs. Honor De Tracy about 1215. They were the parents of at least 1 son."},"et":{"1185–":"1185–Surnud","1167–1230":"1167–1230","1170–Female":"1170–Surnud","1172–Male":"1172–Surnud","1175–1195":"1175–1195","1175–1210":"1175–1210","1180–1274":"1180–1274","1184–Female":"1184–Surnud","1185–Male":"1185–Surnud","1192–1250":"1192–1250","1189–Female":"1189–Surnud","1210–1295":"1210–1295","1133–1210":"1133–1210","1137–1199":"1137–1199","1165":"1165","1185":"1185","1184":"1184","1180":"1180","1259":"1259","1215":"1215","1137":"1137","1210":"1210","1199":"1199","1133":"1133","Abt 1215":"umbes 1215","1274":"1274","1175":"1175","1230":"1230","6 June 2002":"6. juuni 2002","1295":"1295","20 OCT 2006":"20. oktoober 2006","1250":"1250","1195":"1195","1172":"1172","1192":"1192","1170":"1170","1290":"1290","1224":"1224","1189":"1189","1167":"1167","Toddington, Gloucestershire, England":"Toddington, Gloucestershire, England","Gloucestershire, England":"Gloucestershire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1185–":"1185–Kuollut","1167–1230":"1167–1230","1170–Female":"1170–Kuollut","1172–Male":"1172–Kuollut","1175–1195":"1175–1195","1175–12